Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?ata:=20ahci=5Fdwc:=20=E7=94=B1=E7=A1=AC?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=E4=BB=B6=E7=BB=BC=E5=90=88=E5=8F=82=E6=95=B0=E8=87=AA=E5=8A=A8?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=E5=90=AF=E7=94=A8=20FIS-Based=20Switching?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

DWC AHCI IP 在 GPARAM2R 寄存器的 FBS_SUP 位（bit 15）报告该控制器
在芯片综合时是否内置了 FBS 支持。ahci_dwc_check_cap() 已读取此位
但未将其传递给 libahci。

在 fbs_sup 为真时设置 AHCI_HFLAG_YES_FBS，使 libahci 将端口标记为
FBS 可用，无需对每款 SoC 单独列举 compatible。

Signed-off-by: Community Fix <fix@rk3568-nas.local>
---
 drivers/ata/ahci_dwc.c | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/ata/ahci_dwc.c b/drivers/ata/ahci_dwc.c
index 8fb66860d..e7ae405f1 100644
--- a/drivers/ata/ahci_dwc.c
+++ b/drivers/ata/ahci_dwc.c
@@ -205,6 +205,9 @@ static void ahci_dwc_check_cap(struct ahci_host_priv *hpriv)
 			 fbs_pmp);
 	}
 
+	if (fbs_sup)
+		hpriv->flags |= AHCI_HFLAG_YES_FBS;
+
 	for_each_set_bit(i, &port_map, AHCI_MAX_PORTS) {
 		if (!dev_mp && hpriv->saved_port_cap[i] & PORT_CMD_MPSP) {
 			dev_warn(&dpriv->pdev->dev, "MPS incapable port %d\n", i);
